    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of life left? This car is in honest, fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some cosmetic wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, dependable choice that gets the job done. Perfect for anyone seeking value and utility without the premium price tag!",
