      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase by a single owner. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The original alloy wheels are pristine, without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still retains that fresh, new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history and an engine bay so clean it looks untouched. It has never seen rain or snow, ensuring the undercarriage is as immaculate as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
